Installation
------------

For installing using the GNU Build System installation method of source packages,
just open a terminal and type the following commands:

	username@host: dir $ tar -jxf nullify.tar.bz2
	username@host: dir $ cd nullify
	username@host: nullify $ ./configure --prefix=/usr/local
	username@host: nullify $ make
	username@host: nullify $ sudo make install

